text: FK Dunav Stari Banovci () is a football club based in Stari Banovci, Vojvodina, Serbia. They currently compete in the Serbian League Vojvodina, the third level of the national league system. ==History== The club won the Vojvodina League West in the 2010–11 season and took promotion to the Serbian League Vojvodina.
